47:46.264 --> 47:50.235
**

47:50.268 --> 47:51.469
[Door opens]

47:51.502 --> 47:53.204
[Cork pops]

47:59.344 --> 48:01.112
-Hi.
-Hey.

48:01.146 --> 48:02.513
Something smells good.

48:02.547 --> 48:04.916
Sure. It's an old
family recipe.

48:04.950 --> 48:07.585
Oh, well, if anybody wants
capers in their chili,

48:07.618 --> 48:10.188
there's about 14 jars of it
in the fridge.

48:10.221 --> 48:11.556
How dare you.

48:11.589 --> 48:14.092
My father'd leap out
of his grave.

48:14.125 --> 48:16.494
[Chuckles]
-Thank you.

48:16.527 --> 48:19.230
Saw a recipe the other day
called for pineapple in chili.

48:19.264 --> 48:20.598
What?

48:20.631 --> 48:23.068
Can you believe that?
Pineapple? In the --

48:23.101 --> 48:26.271
What the hell is this country
coming to?

48:26.304 --> 48:30.175
[Joanie and Haley
laughing upstairs]

48:32.210 --> 48:34.079
Oh, no, thank you.

48:34.112 --> 48:37.715
So, um...what, uh, happens next?
Who comes for all this stuff?

48:37.748 --> 48:40.218
Uh, there's a company
that takes care

48:40.251 --> 48:42.620
of the sale of the furniture
and things.

48:42.653 --> 48:45.590
[Joanie and Haley laughing]

48:47.458 --> 48:49.060
What's so funny?

48:49.094 --> 48:50.962
It's an inside joke.
You wouldn't get it.

48:50.996 --> 48:52.597
-Oh.
[Both laugh]

48:52.630 --> 48:55.133
-Joe: Haley?
-Mm-hmm?

48:55.166 --> 48:59.237
I'm sorry I couldn't get
your dad's sweater back.

48:59.270 --> 49:01.106
That's okay.

49:06.644 --> 49:10.115
**

49:10.148 --> 49:13.985
**

49:14.019 --> 49:16.454
Joanie: Do you remember when Dad
tried to convince us

49:16.487 --> 49:19.124
that he won a hot-dog eating
contest in Kalamazoo?

49:19.157 --> 49:20.525
Haley: [Laughs]
That wasn't true?

49:20.558 --> 49:21.759
Oh, honey, no.

49:21.792 --> 49:23.628
Why would he
make that up?

49:23.661 --> 49:25.463
I don't know.

49:25.496 --> 49:27.498
I -- I think he thought
it was funny.

49:27.532 --> 49:29.734
-Bos: That's hilarious.
-Dad was such a weirdo.

49:33.804 --> 49:36.041
Hey, Joe,
can you pass the salt?

49:36.074 --> 49:38.176
Yeah.

