50:09.340 --> 50:10.041
Oh, God, no, Mom,
for God's sake,

50:11.742 --> 50:13.811
do not fly back here
for this.

50:13.844 --> 50:15.780
It's...
He'll be back soon.

50:15.813 --> 50:17.782
No, Mo--

50:17.815 --> 50:19.550
God, I should never
have told you.

50:19.584 --> 50:21.186
It's not a big deal.

50:21.219 --> 50:23.288
I think he's just under
a lot of stress, okay?

50:23.321 --> 50:24.555
It's...

50:24.589 --> 50:26.524
He'll be back soon.
[Joanie fusses]

50:26.557 --> 50:29.760
Oh, I know, I know.
He'll be back soon.

50:29.794 --> 50:31.796
He will. I know.

